Recipe: #021 - Falconers Galaxy IPA v2
Brewer: 
Asst Brewer: 
Style: American IPA
TYPE: All Grain
Taste: (30.0) November 28 - 2016 - Not bitter enough. Likely because of the lack of first addition hops. Should have been atleast 80 IBU. Hops are still nice, fruity, citrus, pineapple.
December 6 - 2016 - Awesome orange color. Slight hues of yellow. Aroma: Creamsicle, Mango, Pineapple. Taste: Punchy, Balanced Bitterness. Good malt backbone and balance. Citrus, juice, orange, tangerine.

December 16 - Wicked laced cavernous head. 

